        "description": "Ensures uniform coverage without gaps or excessive overlap heating; 60% recommended for Ti-6Al-4V to achieve even cleaning on curved or irregular surfaces, higher (70-80%) for heavy contamination; source: Process optimization in International Journal of Advanced Manufacturing Technology (2018)."
      }
    }
  },
